body_html: @xiongzhp: Try uninstalling all your torch installations, by repeating pip uninstall torch until it does not find any version anymore. Then build it from source again and see if that resolves the issue. It might be that python refers to the wrong torch. Otherwise, I would refer you to another more knowledgeable person ;)
